export const homeObjOne = {
  id: 'about',
  lightBg: false,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDesc: true,
  topLine: 'Premium Landscaping Services',
  headline: 'Outstanding Service',
  description: 'Our landscape designer will carefully listen to your goals and vision for your outdoor space, and create them to the last detail. We have a passion for what we do and a commitment to doing it right the first time.',
  buttonLabel: 'Get Started',
  imgStart: false,
  img: require('../../images/svg-1.svg').default,
  alt: 'Gardening',
  dark: true,
  primary: true,
  darkText: false
};


export const homeObjTwo = {
  id: 'discover',
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: 'Who We Are',
  headline: 'North East Ohio Lanscapers',
  description: 'Kiss Landscaping Company is a complete professional landscaping service with a wide-range of experience from large commercial properties to smaller custom jobs.',
  buttonLabel: 'Learn More',
  imgStart: true,
  img: require('../../images/svg-2.svg').default,
  alt: 'Park',
  dark: false,
  primary: false,
  darkText: true
};

export const homeObjThree = {
  id: 'about',
  lightBg: false,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDesc: true,
  topLine: 'Landscape Design Services',
  headline: 'From patios and pools, to fire pits, and planting',
  description: 'We can help you pick out colors, textures and materials for all the features of your outdoor living space – from pavers, rock, tile, boulders, stains, paints and much more.',
  buttonLabel: 'Services',
  imgStart: false,
  img: require('../../images/svg-3.svg').default,
  alt: 'Gardening',
  dark: true,
  primary: true,
  darkText: false
};
